text: Jaffueliobryum arsenei is a species of moss in the family Ptychomitriaceae. It is endemic to Querétaro and Zacatecas states in Mexico. It is an Endangered species, threatened by habitat loss. ==References== Category:Bryophyta of North America Category:Endemic flora of Mexico Category:Flora of Querétaro Category:Flora of Zacatecas Category:Endangered biota of Mexico Category:Endangered plants Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot Category:Grimmiales
title: Jaffueliobryum arsenei
